      "Text": "Security update for go1.26-openssl",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for go1.26-openssl fixes the following issues\n\n- Update to version go1.26.5 (bsc#1255111).\n- CVE-2026-39822: os: Root escape via symlink plus trailing slash (bsc#1271014).\n- CVE-2026-42505: crypto/tls: omit PSK in ECH outer client hello (bsc#1271015).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
